The following monograph is in progress:

* Benoit Fresse, _Operads and Grothendieck-TeichmÃ¼ller groups_, [hal-00656333](http://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00656333), [pdf](http://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/docs/00/65/63/33/PDF/OperadGT-January2012Preprint.pdf) - extract for a school, Jan 2012 (200 pages); _Homotopy of operads and GT groups_, December draft [pdf](http://math.univ-lille1.fr/~fresse/OperadHomotopyBook/OperadGT-December2012Preprint.pdf) 317 pp. 

> The ultimate objective of this book is to prove that the Grothendieck-TeichmÃ¼ller group is the group of homotopy automorphisms of a rational completion of the little 2-discs operad.

